::Hevn::
     "Your daughter should be fine.  I left her with her father and the rest of the Maximals when I came after you.  Which, I might add, was not the best move I could've made.  At least from a selfpreservation standpoint."  He turns around and shows Blackstorm his back.  Despite the healing effects of the CR chambers the scars are still visible from the shots he took there.  He then turns back around.  "Needless to say I failed to rescue you."
